{"tid":296832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新假期推介大家去北韓玩","createTime":"2017-06-25T03:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T10:22:16.000Z","uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"056f6fab2979f083007673639135dee8061f6d55","tid":296832,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"睇完洪永城嘅北韓節目，感覺北韓開始沒那麼神秘，但依然有點點唔夠精彩，不如大家自己親身去北韓自己睇一次，真真假假自己決定。剛好香港有學術機構與當地團合作，帶參加者去不同的學校或圖書館同學生交流，特設平壤、 開城市步行時間等，志在讓人深入認識北韓人民的生活，在職人士都可報名！<br />\n<br />\n學術交流：北韓 Open Tour (&ldquo;Nice Meeting You&rdquo; 반갑습니다)<br />\n<br />\n行程：平壤、開城<br />\n住宿：中國(1 晚)酒店及北韓(3 晚)當地酒店<br />\n交通：坐飛機/火車來往北京和朝鮮<br />\n另包：簽證費、膳食、導遊<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"http://www.easternvision.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.easternvision.hk&d=9%2BZN6Ff8PaoQpbDbzc4EizOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a65558d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.easternvision.hk</a><br />\n查詢：Rubio Chan 6102 9223<br />\n<br />\n北韓秋季深度7天團<br />\n<br />\n行程：平壤、平城、南浦、開城<br />\n住宿：中國(飛機團1 晚，火車團2 晚酒店)及北韓(4 晚)當地酒店<br />\n交通：坐飛機/火車來往瀋陽和朝鮮<br />\n另包：簽證費、膳食、導遊<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"http://www.glotravel.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.glotravel.hk&d=9%2BZN6Ff8PaoQpbDbzc4EizOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a33feaee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.glotravel.hk</a><br />\n查詢：Rubio Chan 6102 9223"},{"pid":"566a868742ac464c020adcccedbe1d7113158fce","tid":296832,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637af5597a0e4eeaafbace765112dd64a1a8f25c","tid":296832,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"